<div class="container marketing">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <%= image_tag("Chacos.jpeg", :class => "img-circle",
          :style => "width: 200px; height: 200px;") %>
      <h2 class="mucklucks">mucklucks</h2>
      <p>Mucklucks was created as a haven for travelers and wanderlusters.
         We believe the best travel knowledge comes from people who have been there.
         Through honest opinions, advice, blogs, pictures, and popular travel sites,
         we hope to make travel research easy, collaborative, and fun.</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#featurette3" role="button">More &raquo;</a></p>
