      <p>The public map is the ultimate travel asset.  Simply click on a country of interest
         to glean travel knowledge from other Muckluck users.</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#featurette2" role="button">More &raquo;</a></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <%= image_tag("Myanmar.jpeg", :class => "img-circle",
          :style => "width: 200px; height: 200px;") %>
      <h2>private map</h2>
      <p>The private map is ideal for storing travel photos, blogs, and memories.
         Highlight the countries you have been to, with a personal profile of memories
         attached to each.</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#featurette1" role="button">More &raquo;</a></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
  </div>

