          <span class="index_links"><%= link_to "save", signup_path %></span></h2>
      <p class="lead">Most people keep their travel memories in countless places:
          a blog here, a photo album there...  With the mucklucks private map
          you can gather all your travel memories in one place, organized by country.
          Click countries to change their color so you can visually see countries
          you have been to and countries you have yet to explore!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <%= image_tag("Myanmar.jpeg", :size => "480x320") %>
    </div>
  </div>

